criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

          1. age ≥ 6 years old;

          2. living for above 5 years at present residence.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. resident with coronary angiography (CAG) or endoscopic retrograde
             cholangiopancreatography (ERCP) in 6 months;

          2. resident taking amiodarone drug;

          3. resident with abnormal kidney function or serious illness
